SPSS-Mac-MCP
============

Copyright (c) 2026 Juliet C.L.K. (opalus12138)

This product includes software originally developed by SPSS-MCP Contributors
(https://github.com/Exekiel179/SPSS-MCP), licensed under the MIT License.

This project re-engineers the upstream SPSS-MCP for native macOS support:

  * Adds macOS installation path detection (config.py)
  * Adds DYLD_FALLBACK_LIBRARY_PATH handling to work around macOS SIP
    restrictions on DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH (spss_engine.py)
  * Adapts Python site-packages path resolution for SPSS macOS layout
    (Resources/Python3/lib/python3.X/site-packages)
  * Validates 23 SPSS analysis methods end-to-end on macOS

